om/teacher.php?id=73\'>Blox</a>','manual',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2016-08-03 12:29:48',NULL,NULL,'Back plank pop to hand to hand ',''),(792,559,1,'High side star','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'','<iframe width=\'560\' height=\'315\' src=\'//www.youtube.com/embed/O1h2CuVlKbw?rel=0\' frameborder=\'0\' allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n<br><br>\r\nbase: <a href=\'http://partneracrobatics.com/teacher.php?id=56\'>Martin Kvist</a><br>\r\nflyer: \r\n<a href=\'#\'>Vanille</a>','manual',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2016-09-13 19:30:40',NULL,NULL,'',''),(321,0,1,'home_page_main','home_page_main',NULL,NULL,NULL,'This one is the main text in the home page','<br>\nThe sport of partner acrobatics is an exciting practice has been performed around the world for hundreds of years.  The practice involves two or more people, with one person as the \'base\' (in standing or lying position), lifting, moving and supporting another person as a \'flyer\'. The poses/skills can be static or dynamic and can be practiced one-off, in a sequence, or in a whole show.  It is simply loads of fun. \n<br>\n<br>\n<b>We offer three types of trainings:</b>\n<br>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<!-- <a href=\'/program-15a.php\'>Advanced Intensive</a>new dates coming soon<br> -->\n<a href=\'/program-thai.php\'>Intensive Training</a> - 2 weeks long. Next one is in Thailand, January 3-16, 2017<br>\n<a href=\'/program-15.php\'>Intensive Training</a> - 1 or 2 weeks long. Next one is in Spain, June 8-21, 2017<br>\n<a href=\'/program-tt.php\'>Teacher Training</a> - Month long. Next one is in Spain, August 1-28, 2017<br>\n</ul><br>\n\n Our Partner Acrobatics programs cover many different acrobatic disciplines, including: <b>standing acrobatics, handstand training, washing machines, trio tricks, icarian games and much more.</b> This physical intensity of our program is balanced out with our therapeutic sessions that aim to heal and restore the body.\n <br>\n<br>\n\nAt the heart of our training programs is the concept of sustainability of the physical body – the use of proper alignment and the principles of sports science to increase performance and decrease the risk of pain and/or injury.\n <br>\n\nThis element of our trainings is weaved into our <b>Prehab program</b> – a selection of exercises specifically aimed at promoting injury prevention, structural integration and correct movement technique for long-term physical health and fitness. These include postural realignment exercises, resistance training and correct breathing techniques.\n <br> <br>\n\nDuring our courses we often concurrently run 3 classes at a time, giving the students the option to choose between: standing acro, L basing and therapeutics.  \nOur therapeutic options include Thai Massage along with <b>Flying Therapeutics</b> and the <b>One Minute Practice. </b><br>\nFlying Therapeutics is a bodywork practice where the receiver (flyer) benefits from a weightless,\ninverted and restorative treatment.\nIt helps induce a deep and comforting connection with one’s inner child. For more information and videos, visit <a href=\'http://www.flyingtherapeutics.org\' target=\'_blank\'>www.flyingtherapeutics.org</a>.<br>\nThe One Minute Practice  is a self care system empowering people to treat themselves using breath and micromovements. For more more information, visit <a href=\'http://one-minute-practice.com/en/\' target=\'_blank\'>www.one-minute-practice.com</a>.<br>\n<br>\n\n<h4>Who’ s this practice for?</h4><br>\n<ul>Amateur acrobats.<br>\n\nPractitioners of Acroyoga, Partner Yoga, Acrosage, Inversion Therapy, Tulayoga wishing to enhance their skills.<br>\n\nExisting teachers that want to train intensively as a student.<br>\n\nCircus artists that want to improve their practice with partners or groups.<br>\n\nAnyone with passion and determination to have fun.<br>\n\nYou?</ul>','pages',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2016-10-05 04:23:06',NULL,NULL,'','<p>Hola!<br>\r\n<b>Emily</b>, <b>Niko</b> y <b>Lorenzo</b> os dan la bienvenida a esta página web. <br><br>\r\n<b>Partner Acrobatics</b> es una práctica que se compone de 2 o más personas; una persona como la base o portor que levanta y apoya al volador o ágil en posturas y secuencias estáticas o dinámicas. La base puede practicar en posición estirada o de pie.\r\n<br>\r\nPura diversión !!!</p> \r\n<p>\r\nOfrecemos dos tipos de cursos:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\'program-tt.php\'>Formación de profesores</a> - 4 semanas. España. Enero de 2015.\r\n<li><a href=\'program-15.php\'><!---->Curso Intensivo</a><!----> - 1 o 2 semanas de duración. Tailandia. Agosto 2015.\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>En nuestros cursos de formación también ofrecemos\r\n<b>Flying Therapeutics</b> que es una práctica donde el que recibe se beneficia de un tratamiento en inversion, suspendido y confortable.\r\nAyuda a inducir una conexión profunda y reconfortante con el niño interior.\r\n<br> Más información y vídeos <a href=\'http://www.flyingtherapeutics.org\' target=\'_blank\'>www.flyingtherapeutics.org</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>¿Para quién es esta práctica? </h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Acróbatas principiantes.\r\n<li>Los practicantes de Acroyoga, Yoga en pareja, Acrosage, Inversion Therapy, Tulayoga que deseen mejorar sus habilidades.\r\n<li>Profesores que quieran perfeccionar sus habilidades.\r\n<li>Artistas de circo que quieran mejorar su práctica con sus parejas o grupos.\r\n<li>Cualquier persona con pasión y determinación para divertirse.\r\n<li>Eres tu?\r\n\r\n</ul>'),(322,0,1,'home_page_testimonials','home_page_testimonials',NULL,NULL,NULL,'The text about the Testimonials on the Home Page','<p><i>\'\'This course went beyond my expectations, I loved every single moment. I really apreciated the teachers passion for acro and their teaching styles. It doesnt matter if you´re a beginner or advanced, this is for everybody who enjoys acro.\'\'</i></p>\r\n<p><i>\'\'During this intense month I learned a lot about acrobatics, therapeutic bodywork,\r\n myself and about being in a group. This course is a life-changing event!\'\'</i></p>\r\n<p><i>\'\'The Partner Acrobatics & Flying Therapeutics course was many different flavours of awesome.<br>\r\n For acro junkies like me, it\'s incredible how quickly you can progress and up skill when you train six or seven hours every day for a month. <br>\r\n Niko, Lorenzo, Emily and Mimi are talented, real, hilarious and totally committed to everyone\'s progress.\r\n   Expect laughter, frustration, sweat, support, breakthroughs and moments of glory.\'\'</i></p>','pages',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2015-04-28 17:31:06',NULL,NULL,'','<p><i>\'\'Este curso fue más allá de mis expectativas, me encantó en cada momento. Realmente se DISFRUTA la pasión de los profes de acro y sus diferentes estilos de enseñanza. No importa si eres un principiante o avanzado, esto es para todo aquel que disfruta del acro.\'\'</i></p>\r\n<p><i>\'\'Durante este intenso mes he aprendido mucho acerca de la acrobacia, del Vuelo Terapeutico, y de mí mismo. Este curso es un evento que cambia la vida!\'\'</i></p>\r\n<p><i>\'\'El curso Partner Acrobatics y Vuelo Terapeutico fue lleno de preciosas sensaciones.\r\nPara adictos de la acrobacia como yo, es increíble lo rápido que uno puede progresar con sus habilidadades cuando se entrena seis o siete horas cada día durante un mes.<br>\r\nNiko, Lorenzo, Emily y Mimi son talentosos, reales, divertidos y totalmente comprometidos con el progreso de todos. Cuenta con risas,  frustraciones, sudor, el apoyo, avances y momentos de gloria.\'\'</i></p>'),(323,0,1,'mexico_program_main','mexico_program_main',NULL,NULL,NULL,'','<h3>Teachers</h3>\n<!--<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=52\'><span class=\'teacherIcon fons\'> </span><div><span class=\'teacherName \'>Fons<span></a> - The legend..The teacher of the teachers</div></div>-->\n<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=33\'><span class=\'teacherIcon emily\'> </span><div><span class=\'teacherName \'>Emily Baxter<span></a> -  Super mama, loves party time</div></div>\n<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'te