s, Icarians, etc. </p>\n  <p><span class=\'progTherapy\'>Therapeutic Practice</span>: a mix of thai massage, <a href=\'http://flyingtherapeutics.org/\' target=\'_blank\'>Flying Therapeutics</a>, <a href=\'http://one-minute-practice.com\' target=\'_blank\'>One Minute Practice</a> to enjoy resting and recovering.</p>\n<p><span class=\'progTeaching\'>Teaching</span>: time dedicated to grow your skills as a teacher.</p>\n<p><span class=\'progLecture\'>Lecture</span>: from sport science to marketing, perfecting  your knowledge as a practitioner and teacher.</p>\n<p><span class=\'progOptional\'>Optional</span>: this time is dedicated to volunteers that want to share some special skills with the rest of the group or do your own practice.</p>\n<p><span class=\'progWarmUp\'>Warm Up</span>: the best practice to prepare your training day.</p>\n<p><span class=\'progFood\'>Food</span>: mostly vegetarian meals.</p>\n<p><span class=\'progOffTime\'>Off Time</span>: sometimes we can also rest :)</p>\n</div>\n','pages',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2016-11-05 10:39:22',NULL,NULL,'','<h3>Profes</h3>\r\n<!--<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=52\'><span class=\'teacherIcon fons\'> </span><div><span class=\'teacherName \'>Fons<span></a> - la leyenda...el profe de los profes</div></div>-->\r\n<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=33\'><span class=\'teacherIcon emily\'> </span><div><span class=\'teacherName \'>Emily Baxter<span></a> -  la mamasota, le encanta el festeo.</div></div>\r\n<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=34\'><span class=\'teacherIcon niko\'> </span><div><span class=\'teacherName \'>Niko Douwes<span></a> - sargente del acro</div></div>\r\n<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=32\'><span class=\'teacherIcon lorenzo\'> </span><div><span class=\'teacherName \'>Lorenzo Becchi<span></a>  - abuelo, \'el terapeuta\'</div></div>\r\n<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=36\'><span class=\'teacherIcon mimi\'> </span><div><span clas