g Machines, Dutch Acro, Therapeutics, Icarian etc.</p>\n<p><span class=\'progHandstand\'>Handstand</span>: Two choices running simultaneously either beg-intermediate focusing on alignment and conditioning or the inter-vanced focusing more on variations and progressions toward one arm. </p>\n  <p><span class=\'progFoundations\'>Foundations</span>: Acrobatic skills that everyone has to master.</p>\n<p><span class=\'progFood\'>Food</span>: Mostly vegetarian meals.</p>\n  <p><span class=\'progTherapy\'>Therapeutics</span>: A mix of Thai massage, <a href=\'http://flyingtherapeutics.org/\' target=\'_blank\'>Flying Therapeutics</a> or <a href=\'http://one-minute-practice.com\' target=\'_blank\'>One Minute Practice</a> for active recovery.</p>\n<p><span class=\'progLecture\'>Lecture</span>: Sport science, prehab and sustainability in your practice.</p>\n<p><span class=\'progOffTime\'>Off Time</span>: Sometimes we can also rest :)</p>\n</div>','pages',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2016-10-08 07:29:28',NULL,NULL,'thai_program_main','<h3>Profes</h3>\r\n<!--<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=52\'><span class=\'teacherIcon fons\'> </span><div><span class=\'teacherName \'>Fons<span></a> - la leyenda...el profe de los profes</div></div>-->\r\n<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=33\'><span class=\'teacherIcon emily\'> </span><div><span class=\'teacherName \'>Emily Baxter<span></a> -  la mamasota, le encanta el festeo.</div></div>\r\n<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=34\'><span class=\'teacherIcon niko\'> </span><div><span class=\'teacherName \'>Niko Douwes<span></a> - sargente del acro</div></div>\r\n<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=32\'><span class=\'teacherIcon lorenzo\'> </span><div><span class=\'teacherName \'>Lorenzo Becchi<span></a>  - abuelo, \'el terapeuta\'</div></div>\r\n<div class=\'teacherLI\'><a href=\'teacher.php?id=36\'><span class=\'teacherIcon mimi\'> </span><div><span class=\'teacherName \'>Mimi Nuñez<span></a> -  